out1 <- rpmodel( 
  tc             = 20,           # temperature, deg C
  vpd            = 1000,         # Pa,
  co2            = 400,          # ppm,
  fapar          = 1,            # fraction  ,
  ppfd           = 30,           # mol/m2/d,
  elv            = 0,            # m.a.s.l.,
  do_ftemp_kphio = FALSE,
  do_soilmstress = TRUE,
  soilm          = 0.2,
  apar_soilm     = 0.1,
  bpar_soilm     = 0.7,
  meanalpha      = 0.2 
  )

out2 <- rpmodel( 
  tc             = 20,           # temperature, deg C
  vpd            = 1000,         # Pa,
  co2            = 400,          # ppm,
  fapar          = 1,            # fraction  ,
  ppfd           = 30,           # mol/m2/d,
  elv            = 0,            # m.a.s.l.,
  do_ftemp_kphio = c(FALSE, TRUE),
  do_soilmstress = TRUE,
  soilm          = 0.2,
  apar_soilm     = 0.1,
  bpar_soilm     = 0.7,
  meanalpha      = 0.2 
  )
